{"type": "article", "id": 6265, "title": "模拟山羊 Goat Simulator", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 3603, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;\">羊年到了，怎么也要为您推荐一款跟羊有关的游戏，那就是去年大红大紫的《模拟山羊》。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604214008n1pgsXPKOjReYlFC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t这只山羊可和你想象的萌萌的小绵羊不同，看它那张痴汉脸就明白，这只山羊一定是个绅（hen）士（tai）。西方语境里的山羊可不是什么好角，希腊神话中半人半羊的萨堤尔可是个色情狂，山羊也是叛逆的象征。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t所以你大概知道这游戏是个什么路数了吧，扮演一只山羊，在小镇里横冲直撞。“这是一个<span style=\"color:#000000;\">愚蠢的游戏”，但超级有趣。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#000000;\">更详细的介绍请戳</span><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/display/articles/5685.html\" style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;color:#0069D6;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">这里</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}